    "en": {
      "title": "Kimbula-Ele Guna\u2019s associates arrested with KG, Heroin",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka Police arrested two men who were operating the drug network of notorius underworld drug trafficker 'Kimbula-Ele Guna' (Real Name: Sinniah Gunasekaram).",
        "The arrests were made during special raid by the Police Special Task Force in Palliyawatte, Wattala on Thursday (28) night.",
        "A live hand grenade, Kerala Cannabis, and Heroin were seized from the possession of the suspects who are residents from Colombo 15.",
        "India says it will protect its interests as Chinese boat heads to Sri Lanka",
        "Parliament prorogued with effect from today (28); Next session on 3rd August"
      ],
